id%20to%20stabilize%20the%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20announced%20on%20Friday%20it%20had%20selected%20bidders%20for%20almost%20142%2C000%20tons%20of%20rice%20from%20the%20government%20reserve%2C%20local%20media%20reported.%20Bidders%20are%20paying%2021%2C217%20yen%20(about%20%24143)%20per%2060%20kilograms%20and%20the%20extra%20supplies%20are%20expected%20to%20start%20reaching%20stores%20later%20this%20month.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EReleasing%20such%20a%20large%20amount%20of%20rice%20would%20improve%20the%20%26quot%3Bsupply-demand%20balance%2C%26quot%3B%20agriculture%20minister%20Taku%20Eto%20told%20a%20press%20conference.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20the%20ministry%20would%20carry%20out%20another%20auction%20later%20this%20month.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fhow-to-cook-rice%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERice%3C%2Fa%3E%20supplies%20in%20Japan%20started%20to%20decline%20last%20summer%2C%20sending%20prices%20sharply%20higher.%20Experts%20have%20blamed%20the%20problem%20on%20high%20temperatures%20in%202023%20damaging%20crops%2C%20and%20stockpiling%20over%20fears%20of%20an%20earthquake%20%E2%80%94%20and%20expectations%20that%20prices%20would%20keep%20rising.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20intervention%2C%20the%20agriculture%20ministry%20said%20a%205-kilogram%20bag%20of%20rice%20cost%20an%20average%20of%204%2C077%20yen%20(about%20%2427)%20at%20some%201%2C000%20stores%20in%20the%20week%20ending%20March%209.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20almost%20double%20the%20price%20this%20time%20last%20year%20and%20marks%20the%2010th%20consecutive%20weekly%20increase.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECore%20consumer%20price%20index%20data%20released%20by%20Japan's%20internal%20affairs%20ministry%20at%20the%20end%20of%20January%20showed%20that%20the%20price%20of%20rice%20rose%20nearly%2071%25%20year-on-year%20in%20Tokyo's%2023%20wards.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20231%2C000%20tons%20of%20rice%20authorized%20to%20be%20released%20from%20the%20stockpile%20represents%20about%2020%25%20of%20the%20total%2C%20The%20New%20York%20Times%20reported.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-rice-prices-shortage-auction-tokyo-agriculture-ministry-stockpile-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742211348000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d807eab8b41a9673fad072%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-rice-prices-shortage-auction-tokyo-agriculture-ministry-stockpile-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Japanese%20government%20is%20releasing%20supplies%20from%20its%20emergency%20rice%20stockpile%20for%20the%20first%20time%20to%20address%20shortages%20that%20have%20sparked%20price%20rises.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nredmond%40insider.com%20(Nora%20Redmond)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-rice-prices-shortage-auction-tokyo-agriculture-ministry-stockpile-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Game%20of%20Gods%E2%80%99%20Getting%20Film%20Adaptation%20From%20Italy%E2%80%99s%20Rainbow%20Group%20and%20Wattpad%20Webtoon%20Studios%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742211328000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2FGame-of-Gods-1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236339162%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Italy%E2%80%99s%20Rainbow%20Group%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20behind%20the%20hit%20%E2%80%9CWinx%20Club%E2%80%9D%20animation%20franchise%20%E2%80%94%20has%20optioned%20the%20rights%20to%20adapt%20mythological%20saga%20%E2%80%9CGame%20of%20Gods%2C%E2%80%9D%20which%C2%A0has%20drawn%20millions%20of%20young%20adult%20readers%20on%20user-generated%20fiction%20platform%20Wattpad.%20The%20%E2%80%9CGame%20of%20