20San%20Gabriel%20Mountains%20near%20where%20I%20live%2C%20I%20had%20a%20hard%20time%20getting%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fbest-renters-insurance-companies%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Erenters%20insurance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20No%20insurance%20company%20would%20cover%20my%20tiny%20cabin%20as%20I%20was%20considered%20a%20high%20risk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFast-forward%20to%20last%20year.%20While%20I%20had%20reinstated%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Faaa-home-insurance-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAAA%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20renters%20insurance%2C%20I%20was%20considering%20whether%20I%20needed%20it%20or%20not.%20Thankfully%2C%20I%20decided%20to%20renew%20my%20policy.%20In%20January%2C%20when%20the%20Eaton%20Fire%20in%20Altadena%20ignited%2C%20destroying%20thousands%20of%20homes%20and%20displacing%20thousands%20of%20families%2C%20I%20had%20to%20evacuate.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI'm%20glad%20I%20did%2C%20as%20the%20coverage%20helped%20pay%20for%20some%20of%20my%20living%20expenses%20while%20I%20was%20away%20and%20also%20covered%20cleaning%20my%20place%20of%20the%20ash%20and%20debris%20from%20the%20fire.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%223d578b9e-0044-46ea-93f1-3675459214c6%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20checked%20the%20details%20of%20my%20policy%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20my%20zone%20received%20a%20mandatory%20evacuation%20order%2C%20I%20double-checked%20the%20details%20of%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhomeowners-insurance%2Fwhat-is-renters-insurance%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ewhat%20my%20renters%20insurance%20policy%20covers%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20As%20renter's%20insurance%20is%20essentially%20contents%20insurance%20and%20doesn't%20cover%20the%20structure%20of%20the%20property%2C%20repair%2C%20restoration%2C%20and%20replacement%20of%20my%20belongings%20were%20included%20in%20my%20policy.%20I%20am%20covered%20for%20up%20to%20%2433%2C000%20per%20occurrence%20for%20the%20unscheduled%20personal%20property.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELoss%20of%20use%20was%20also%20included%20in%20my%20renters%20insurance%20policy.%20This%20means%20that%20if%20my%20home%20was%20uninhabitable%20for%20any%20reason%20%E2%80%94%20including%20evacuations%20and%20displacement%20%E2%80%94%20certain%20expenses%20could%20be%20covered.%20I%20am%20covered%20up%20to%20%246%2C600%20for%20loss%20of%20use%20per%20occurrence.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20typically%20includes%20meals%20and%20food%20expenses%20that%20exceed%20your%20regular%20spending%2C%20accommodations%20such%20as%20staying%20in%20an%20Airbnb%20or%20hotel%2C%20and%20other%20living%20costs%20that%20I%20incurred%20because%20I%20couldn't%20live%20at%20my%20place.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2263ef3a13-89f6-4df9-a569-0db23bb9bb61%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20spoke%20with%20an%20insurance%20adjuster%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20answered%20a%20short%20series%20of%20questions%20on%20the%20AAA%20app%20to%20file%20my%20claim.%20A%20few%20days%20later%2C%20I%20received%20a%20notification%20that%20I%20was%20assigned%20a%20claim%20number%2C%20an%20insurance%20adjuster%2C%20and%20their%20contact%20information.%20I%20gave%20them%20a%20ring.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAfter%20talking%20to%20them%2C%20they%20arranged%20for%20a%20vendor%20that%20specializes%20in%20restoration%20for%20a%20home%20visit.%20They%20would%20give%20me%20an%20estimate%20on%20how%20much%20it%20would%20cost%20to%20clean%20my%20textiles%20(everything%20from%20clothing%20to%20couch%20cushions)%20and%20clean%20my%20place%20of%20the%20ash%20and%20soot.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225d60c313-2761-4d96-9bd4-193f542ed854%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20documented%20as%20much%20as%20I%20could%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20night%20I%20had%20to%20evacuate%2C%20the%20canyon%20area%20where%20I%20lived%20was%20experiencing%20strong%20gusts%20of%20wind%20as%20fast%20as%2090%20miles%20per%20hour.%20When%20I%20heard%20a%20fire%20broke%20out%20in%20the%20neighboring%20city%20of%20Altadena%2C%20I%20was%20optimistic%20I%20would%20return%20the%20following%20day.%20That%20changed%20quickly%20as%20the%20fire%20spread%20rapidly%20toward%20the%20mountains%20above%20me.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20a%20precautionary%20measure%2C%20I%20took%20photos%20and%20videos%20of%20my%20belongings%2C%20including%20my%20furniture%2C%20artwork%2C%20clothing%2C%20kitchenware%2C%20and%20sticker%20collection.%20I%20also%20took%20screenshots%20of%20notifications%20of%20the%20city-mandated%20evacuation%20order%2C%20and%20when%20the%20order%20was%20lifted.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20also%20kept%20receipts%20and%20took%20screenshots%20of%20my%20receipts%20for%20purchases%20that%20could%20be%20covered%3A%20food%20and%20supplies%20for%20my%20cat%2C%20grocery%20receipts%20and%20restaurant%20bills%2C%20and%20other%20potentially%20covered%20living%20expenses.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274febcee-278f-42b5-900f-c73e34fc738b%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EMy%20claim%20payout%20will%20arrive%20in%20installments%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20I%20was%20still%20submitting%20my%20loss%20of%20use%20expenses%2C%20I%20received%20a%20partial%20payout%20for%20the%20remediation%20and%20cleanup%20coverage%2C%20which%20is%20technically%20under%20the%20unscheduled%20personal%20property%20part%20of%20my%20claim.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20received%20an%20email%20from%20AAA%20asking%20for%20my%20direct%20deposit%20information.%20Once%20I%20provided%20it%2C%20the%20funds%20were%20deposited%20into%20my%20linked%20bank%20account%20the%20same%20day.%20My%20%24250%20deductible%20was%20taken%20from%20that%20amount.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f79aef44-52ad-4e8d-885c-0267eaf52541%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20considered%20boosting%20my%20policy%20amounts%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20increasing%20my%20policy%20limits%20would%20likely%20be%20much%20more%20expensive%2C%20I%20have%20considered%20whether%20it's%20worth%20it%20to%20see%20if%20I%20can%20add%20a%20rider%20that%20would%20cover%20spoiled%20food.%20I%20reached%20out%20to%20AAA%20and%20talked%20to%20an%20insurance%20rep.%20As%20expected%2C%20there%20was%20an%20insurance%20moratorium%20for%20my%20ZIP%20code.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20the%20insurance%20company%20had%20put%20a%20stop%20on%20issuing%20new%20policies%20or%20expanding%20coverage%20on%20new%20ones.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20realized%20how%20expensive%20it%20would%20be%20to%20repair%20or%20replace%20everything%20and%20how%20I%20likely%20underestimated%20how%20much%20insurance%20I%20needed.%20Last%20year%2C%20I%20paid%20%24253%20for%20my%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fauto-insurance%2Fwhat-is-an-insurance-premium%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Epremium%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20or%20%2422%20a%20month%20(plus%20a%20%24250%20deductible).%20In%20case%20there%20are%20more%20covered%20natural%20disasters%20this%20year%2C%20I%20want%20to%20make%20sure%20I%20have%20sufficient%20coverage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frenters-insurance-reimbursed-me-quickly-after-la-wildfire-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742209921000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67d48cce69253ccddf995aa4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frenters-in