20is%20possible%20using%20classical%20computers%2C%20with%20researchers%20optimistic%20it%20could%20revolutionize%20medicine%2C%20data%20privacy%2C%20and%20more.%20Advancement%20in%20the%20field%20relies%20both%20on%20hardware%20research%20and%20software%20and%20algorithmic%20development%C2%A0%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20the%20quantum%20business%20is%20booming.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20research%20by%20Boston%20Consulting%20Group%2C%20the%20industry%20attracted%20%241.2%20billion%20from%20venture%20capitalists%20in%202023%20despite%20a%2050%25%20drop%20in%20overall%20tech%20investments%20that%20year.%20BCG%20projects%20that%20quantum%20computing%20will%20create%20between%20%24450%20billion%20and%20%24850%20billion%20of%20economic%20value%20globally%20and%20sustain%20a%20%2490-%24170%20billion%20market%20for%20hardware%20and%20software%20providers%20by%20the%20year%202040.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELinkedIn%20shows%20that%20the%20salary%20bands%20for%20jobs%20in%20quantum%20computing%20range%20from%20%24150%2C000%20on%20the%20low%20end%20and%20balloon%20well%20past%20%24500%2C000%20a%20year%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20role%20and%20company.%20So%20what%20does%20it%20take%20to%20break%20into%20this%20growing%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20lucrative%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0field%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOren%20is%20the%20managing%20director%20of%20SAP%20Labs%20US%20and%20the%20global%20head%20of%20its%20business%20technology%20innovation%20team.%20SAP%2C%20the%20world's%20largest%20non-American%20software%20company%20by%20revenue%2C%20is%20a%20leader%20in%20cloud-based%20quantum%20computing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20recruiters%20in%20the%20field%20look%20for%20curiosity%20more%20than%20anything%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20we%20need%20expertise%20%E2%80%94%20and%20quantum%20is%20a%20very%20deep%20science%20and%20practice%20that%20requires%20a%20lot%20of%20knowledge%20%E2%80%94%20but%20if%20you%20follow%20the%20industry%2C%20you%20see%20there%20are%2