%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fworld%2Ffreed-israeli-hostage-speaks-first-time-about-his-505-days-surviving-hamas-hell%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EFox%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0that%20Hamas%20operatives%20would%20dig%20constantly%2C%20adding%20they%20never%20stopped%2C%20%26quot%3Bnot%20for%20a%20single%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20network%2C%20named%20the%20%26quot%3BGaza%20metro%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20Israeli%20military%2C%20is%20estimated%20to%20be%20around%20560%20-%20720%20km%20long%2C%20with%20approximately%205%2C700%20separate%20shafts%20leading%20down%20to%20the%20tunnels.%20It%20is%20believed%20to%20stretch%20across%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%2C%20with%20tunnels%20connecting%20various%20areas%2C%20including%20military%20bases%2C%20logistics%20centres%2C%20and%20residential%20neighbourhoods.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tunnels%20are%20dug%20by%20hand%2C%20using%20simple%20tools%2C%20and%20are%20often%20reinforced%20with%20concrete%20and%20iron.%20The%20network%20is%20designed%20to%20provide%20Hamas%20militants%20with%20safe%20passage%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20move%20undetected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Shoham%20was%20kidnapped%20from%20Kibbutz%20Be'eri%20on%20October%207%2C%202023.%20His%20wife%20and%20young%20children%2C%20aged%20four%20and%20eight%2C%20were%20also%20taken%20that%20day%2C%20though%20he%20was%20unaware%20of%20their%20fate%20at%20the%20time.%20Hoping%20to%20protect%20them%2C%20he%20stepped%20outside%20to%20surrender%2C%20only%20to%20be%20surrounded%20by%20around%2040%20armed%20men.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriven%20into%20Gaza%20in%20a%20car%20trunk%2C%20he%20was%20ordered%20to%20kneel%20but%20refused%2C%20telling%20his%20captors%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20kill%20me%2C%20kill%20me%2C%20but%20you%20will%20not%20execute%20me%20like%20ISIS.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20then%20paraded%20through%20Gaza's%20streets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%2050%20days%2C%20Mr%20Shoham%20didn't%20know%20if%20his%20wife%20and%20children