%20terrorism%26quot%3B%20globally.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV%20World%2C%20United%20States'%20Director%20of%20National%20Intelligence%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ftrump-and-pm-modi-focused-on-shared-objectives-tulsi-gabbard-to-ndtv-7941747%5C%22%3ETulsi%20Gabbard%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20longtime%20unfortunate%20persecution%2C%20killing%2C%20and%20abuse%20of%20religious%20minorities%20like%20Hindus%2C%20Buddhists%2C%20Christians%2C%20and%20others%20has%20been%20a%20major%20area%20of%20concern%20for%20the%20US%20government%20and%20President%20Trump%20and%20his%20administration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20the%20new%20Cabinet%20under%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20begun%20talks%20with%20the%20interim%20government%20in%20Bangladesh.%20%26quot%3BThe%20talks%20are%20just%20beginning%20between%20President%20Trump's%20new%20cabinet%20coming%20in%20and%20the%20Government%20of%20Bangladesh%2C%20but%20this%20continues%20to%20remain%20a%20central%20focus%20area%20of%20concern%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20while%20speaking%20about%20the%20rise%20of%20Islamic%20extremism%20and%20terrorist%20elements%20in%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20remarks%20she%20spoke%20about%20the%20ideology%20of%20an%20%26quot%3BIslamic%20Caliphate%26quot%3B%20and%20how%20extremist%20elements%20and%20terror%20groups%20globally%20aim%20for%20such%20an%20outcome.%20%26quot%3BThe%20threat%20of%20Islamist%20terrorists%20and%20the%20global%20effort%20of%20different%20terror%20groups%20are%20routed%20in%20the%20same%20ideology%20and%20objective%20-%20which%20is%20to%20rule%20or%20govern%20with%20an%20Islamist%20Caliphate%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20%26quot%3BThis%20obviously%20affects%20people%20of%20any%20other%20religion%2C%20other%20than%20the%20one%20that%20they%20find%20acceptable%2C%20and%20they%20chose%20to%20carry%20this%20out%20with%20terror%20and%20very%20violent%20ways%20and%20means.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Gabbard%20went%20on%20to%20say%20that%20Donald%20Trump%20is%20determined%20to%20identify%20and%20defeat%20such%20an%20ideology%20and%20end%20the%20rise%20of%20what%20he%20calls%20%26quot%3Bradical%20Islamic%20terrorism%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Trump%20remains%20committed%20to%20identifying%20the%20ideology%20that%20drives%20Islamist%20terrorism%2C%20and%20working%20to%20defeat%20this%20ideology%20and%20their%20ability%20exact%20that%20terror%20on%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Gabbard%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20the%20violence%20and%20religious%20persecution%20in%20Bangladesh%2C%20its%20growing%20synergy%20with%20Pakistan's%20notorious%20ISI%20has%20become%20a%20major%20cause%20of%20concern%20over%20the%20last%20two%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELast%20month%20Indian%20Army%20chief%20General%20Upendra%20Dwivedi%20stated%20that%20he%20was%20concerned%20about%20the%20presence%20of%20ISI%20officials%20in%20Bangladesh%20areas%20close%20to%20India's%20border%20regions%2C%20especially%20the%20Siliguri%20corridor.%20Speaking%20to%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20General%20Dwivedi%20said%20that%20they%20must%20make%20sure%20that%20those%20anti-India%20elements%20must%20not%20be%20able%20to%20use%20that%20soil%20to%20send%20terrorists%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20had%20used%20the%20word%20epicentre%20of%20terrorism%20for%20a%20particular%20country%20(Pakistan).%20Now%20those%20countrymen%2C%20if%20they%20go%20to%20any%20other%20place%20and%20they%20happen%20to%20be%20our%20neighbor%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20am%20concerned%2C%20I%20should%20be%20concerned%20about%20it.%20That%20they%20should%20not%20be%20able%20to%20use%20that%20soil%20to%20send%20terrorists%20to%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20General%20Dwivedi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20PM%20Modi%20and%20Donald%20Trump%20met%20in%20Washington%20in%20February%2C%20the%20US%20President%20had%20said%20that%2