coming%2C%20%5Bbut%5D%20we%20did%20not%20expect%20them%20to%20be%20rolled%20out%2Fforced%20upon%20us%20in%20this%20fashion%2C%20nor%20did%20we%20expect%20to%20see%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20to%20be%20countries%20that%20would%20be%20affected%20by%20these%20tariffs%2C%26quot%3B%20one%20CEO%20who%20spoke%20to%20the%20magazine%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20Fortune%20500%20CEO%20told%20Fortune%20last%20week%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20don't%20trust%20that%20what's%20said%20today%20will%20be%20true%20tomorrow.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFoxconn%20CEO%20Young%20Liu%20said%20in%20a%20recent%20earnings%20call%20that%20tariffs%20were%20causing%20chief%20executives%20%26quot%3Ba%20big%20headache.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BJudging%20by%20the%20attitude%20and%20the%20approach%20we%20see%20the%20US%20government%20taking%20towards%20tariffs%2C%20it%20is%20very%2C%20very%20hard%20to%20predict%20how%20things%20will%20develop%20over%20the%20next%20year%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20levied%2025%25%20tariffs%20against%20most%20imports%20from%20Canada%20and%20Mexico%20on%20March%204.%20On%20March%205%2C%20he%20suspended%20those%20tariffs%20for%20automobiles%20covered%20by%20the%20US-Mexico-Canada%20trade%20agreement.%20On%20March%206%2C%20Trump%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-mexico-tariffs-pause-usmca-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eextended%20the%20suspensions%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20all%20goods%20covered%20by%20the%20agreement%20until%20April%202.%20China%20and%20Canada%20responded%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-retaliate-trump-trade-war-tariffs-soybeans-agriculture-two-sessions-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretaliatory%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20president%20then%20placed%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20all%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Feurope-us-trump-trade-war-tariffs-countermeasures-aluminum-steel-