20consumers%2C%20who%20drive%20much%20of%20the%20spending%2C%20and%20the%20broader%20economy.%20Consumer%20spending%20makes%20up%20about%20two-thirds%20of%20GDP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20consumer%2C%20because%20of%20the%20incredibly%20large%20portion%20of%20consumer%20spending%20that's%20coming%20from%20the%2060%20to%2080-year-old%20baby%20boomer%20group%2C%20is%20automatically%20damaged%20by%20what%20goes%20on%20in%20the%20stock%20market%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20stocks%20go%20down%2010%25%2C%20all%20of%20those%20people%20feeling%20flush%20are%20suddenly%20feeling%20less%20flush.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERecession%20fears%20have%20risen%20over%20the%20last%20few%20weeks%20as%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20has%20placed%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%2C%20China%2C%20Mexico%2C%20and%20the%20European%20Union%2C%20creating%20uncertainty%20for%20businesses%20and%20sinking%20consumer%20sentiment.%20The%20economic%20worries%20come%20on%20top%20of%20a%20re-rating%20happening%20in%20the%20technology%20sector%20as%20cheap%20AI%20chatbots%20call%20into%20question%20the%20hefty%20investments%20being%20made%20in%20the%20industry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmead%20manages%20the%20Smead%20Value%20Fund%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Ffunds%2Fsmead-value-fund-investor-class-us83178c8819%3FmiRedirects%3D1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESMVLX%3C%2Fa%3E)%20and%20is%20positioned%20away%20from%20the%20tech%20sector.%20The%20fund%20has%20had%20a%20rough%2012%20months%2C%20falling%208.5%25%20while%20the%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20has%20risen%209.3%25.%20But%20Smead's%20long-term%20track%20record%20is%20impressive%2C%20beating%2096%25%20of%20similar%20funds%20over%20a%2015-year%20period%2C%20according%20to%20Morningstar%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20he%20published%20a%20note%20to%20clients%20that%20sought%20to%20ease%20concerns%20about%20recent%20underperformance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BInvestors%20who%20have%20come%20to%20us%20