2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcedle6je601o.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Farticles%2Fcedle6je601o.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22What's%20%26quot%3BAnother%20Round%26quot%3B%3F%20Big%20Vadodara%20Crash%20Question%20May%20Have%20Danish%20Answer%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruth%20is%20stranger%20than%20fiction.%20And%20sometimes%2C%20more%20tragic.%20Amid%20the%20outrage%20over%20a%20student%20crashing%20a%20car%20into%20three%20vehicles%20in%20Vadodara%2C%20leaving%20a%20woman%20dead%20and%20seven%20others%20injured%2C%20a%20curious%20connection%20has%20emerged%20between%20the%20prime%20accused%20and%20a%20Danish%20movie.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20video%20of%20Rakshit%20Chaurasia%2C%20a%2023-year-old%20law%20student%20at%20Vadodara's%20MS%20University%2C%20exiting%20the%20car%20after%20the%20crash%20and%20screaming%20seemingly%20incoherent%20words%20--%20%26quot%3Banother%20round%26quot%3B%2C%20%26quot%3BNikita%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BOm%20Namah%20Shivay%26quot%3B%20has%20gone%20viral.%20Social%20media%20users%20have%20brainstormed%20what%20these%20words%2C%20particularly%20%26quot%3Banother%20round%26quot%3B%2C%20could%20mean.%20Many%20suspect%20Rakshit%20was%20under%20the%20influence%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Banother%20round%26quot%3B%20meant%20one%20more%20shot.%20Some%20speculated%20that%20he%20could%20have%20meant%20another%20spin%20in%20the%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20search%20by%20the%20police%20at%20his%20home%20has%20opened%20up%20another%20possibility.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20multiple%20news%20reports%2C%20police%20have%20found%20a%20telling%20movie%20poster%20in%20Rakshit's%20rented%20apartment%20in%20Vadodara.%20This%20poster%20is%20of%20the%20Danish%20film%20Druk%2C%20or%20Another%20Round%20in%20English.%20The%20movie%20stars%2C%20among%20others%2C%20Mads%20Mikkelsen%2C%20who%20played%20Le%20Chiffre%20in%20the%20James%20Bond%20film%2C%20Casino%20Royale.%C2%A0Another%20Round%20won%20the%20Oscar%20for%20the%20Best%20International%20Feature%20Film.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20Round%2C%20a%20black%20comedy%20directed%20by%20Thomas%20Vinterberg%2C%20is%20the%20story%20of%20four%20teachers%20struggling%20with%20monotonous%20lives%20and%20unmotivated%20students.%20Then%20one%20day%20they%20come%20across%20a%20theory%20inspired%20by%20the%20work%20of%20a%20Norwegian%20psychiatrist%20that%20humans%20are%20born%20with%20a%20blood%20alcohol%20content%20deficiency.%20The%20teachers%20conclude%20that%20maintaining%20a%20slightly%20higher%20blood%20alcohol%20level%20may%20benefit%20them.%20They%20start%20by%20drinking%20small%20amounts%20through%20the%20day%20and%20get%20the%20desired%20results.%20Over%20time%2C%20they%20push%20the%20boundaries%20before%20the%20drinking%20starts%20adversely%20affecting%20their%20lives.%20Eventually%2C%20one%20of%20them%20dies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20cops%20finding%20the%20movie's%20poster%20at%20Rakshit's%20home%2C%20there%20is%20speculation%20that%20he%20was%20referring%20to%20the%20movie%20when%20he%20screamed%20%26quot%3Banother%20round%26quot%3B.%20According%20to%20investigations%20so%20far%2C%20Rakshit%20has%20a%20four-member%20friends'%20squad.%20The%20others%20are%20Pranshu%2C%20who%20was%20in%20the%20car%20with%20him%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crash%20and%20is%20now%20on%20the%20run%2C%20Suresh%2C%20whose%20home%20they%20visited%20before%20the%20crash%2C%20and%20%26quot%3BNikita%26quot%3B%2C%20a%20name%20he%20kept%20screaming%20after%20the%20accident.%20A%20possible%20theory%20is%20this%20group%20drew%20a%20parallel%20to%20the%20four%20in%20'Another%20Round'%20and%20decided%20to%20follow%20their%20lead.%20There%20is%2C%20however%2C%20an%20interesting%20point.%20In%20the%20movie%2C%20the%20four%20friends%20lay%20down%20some%20ground%20rules%20before%20starting%20the%20drinking%20experiment.%20One%20of%20them%20was%20they%20would%20not%20drink%20and%20drive.%20While%20Rakshit%20has%20claimed%20he%20was%20not%20drunk%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20a%20rapid%20test%20has%20confirmed%20that%20he%20was.%20The%20detailed%20test%20results%20are%20awaited.%20Eyewitnesses%20too%20claim%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bintoxicated%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20crash.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2023-year-old%20has%20been%20charged%20with%20culpable%20homicide%20not%20amounting%20to%20murder%20after%20the%20Volkswagen%20Virtus%20he%20was%20driving%20crashed%20into%20three%20vehicles%2C%20leaving%20a%2035-year-old%20woman%20dead%20and%20seven%20others%20injured.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHemali%20Patel%2C%2035%2C%20and%20Purav%20Patel%2C%2040%2C%20were%20out%20with%20their%20daughter%20after%20Holika%20Dahan%20to%20buy%20colours%20and%20grab%20something%20to%20eat.%20At%20the%20Karelibaug%20area%2C%20the%20car%20Rakshit%20was%20driving%20rammed%20the%20Patels'%20scooter%20and%20two%20other%20vehicles.%20Hemali%2C%20Purav%20and%20their%20daughter%20were%20thrown%20into%20the%20air%20before%20they%20crashed%20to%20the%20ground.%20Hemali%20died%20on%20the%20spot%20and%20Purav%20is%20under%20treatment%20for%20critical%20injuries.%20Their%20little%20daughter%2C%20too%2C%20has%20suffered%20injuries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Patels%20were%20accompanied%20by%20neighbours%20Vikas%20Kevlani%2C%20Jayesh%20and%20Komal%20on%20another%20scooter.%20All%20three%20have%20suffered%20injuries.%20Vikas%20has%20said%20traffic%20fines%20won't%20prevent%20such%20incidents%20caused%20by%20rash%20driving.%20%26quot%3BFine%20is%20not%20the%20solution.%20Only%20if%20there%20is%20strict%20action%20will%20they%20understand%20what%20they%20have%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20youngster%20said%20he%20would%20fight%20the%20matter%20legally.%20%26quot%3BI%20want%20justice.%20Hemaliben%20was%20like%20my%20sister.%20She%20should%20get%20justice%20and%20the%20young%20generation%20should%20know%20the%20impact%20of%20such%20acts%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%