tps%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F119103953.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUS%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20plans%20to%20speak%20with%20Russian%20President%20Vladimir%20Putin%20on%20Tuesday%20regarding%20the%20US-brokered%20ceasefire%20proposal%20for%20the%20war%20in%20Ukraine.%20Trump%20is%20hopeful%20for%20a%20positive%20announcement%2C%20as%20key%20issues%20such%20as%20land%20and%20power%20plants%20have%20been%20discussed.%20The%20focus%20is%20now%20on%20Russia's%20response%20to%20the%20ceasefire%20proposal.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwe-have-a-very-good-chance-trump-to-speak-with-putin-on-us-ceasefire-proposal-for-ukraine%2Farticleshow%2F119103953.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwe-have-a-very-good-chance-trump-to-speak-with-putin-on-us-ceasefire-proposal-for-ukraine%2Famp_articleshow%2F119103953.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwe-have-a-very-good-chance-trump-to-speak-with-putin-on-us-ceasefire-proposal-for-ukraine%2Famp_articleshow%2F119103953.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20After%20The%20Pakistan%20Train%20Terror%3A%20Is%20This%20Just%20The%20Beginning%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20episode%20was%20like%20something%20from%20a%20Wild%20West%20movie%2C%20complete%20with%20a%20desert%20landscape%20and%20heavily%20armed%20fighters.%20In%20fact%2C%20it%20was%20a%20very%20professionally%20managed%20train%20hijack%E2%80%94no%20small%20task%20at%20any%20time%E2%80%94and%20executed%20with%20military%20precision%2C%20with%20women%20and%20children%20released%20immediately%2C%20and%20explicit%20statements%20by%20Pakistani%20soldiers%20released%20as%20%E2%80%9Cprisoners%20of%20war%E2%80%9D.%20That%20says%20something%20about%20the%20group.%20It%20also%20says%20a%20lot%20about%20the%20future%20trajectory.%20This%20is%20serious.%20And%20despite%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20declaring%20that%20the%20operation%20is%20over%2C%20it%20is%20not.%20This%20is%20only%20the%20beginning.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Unfolding%20Drama%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20the%20drama%20have%20now%20been%20telecast%20across%20screens%2C%20with%20the%20attackers%20themselves%20putting%20out%20a%20video%20of%20the%20whole%20saga.%20The%20Balochistan%20Liberation%20Army%20(BLA)%20is%20no%20ordinary%20insurgent%20group.%20Honed%20by%20decades%20of%20violence%20against%20its%20people%2C%20it%20is%20a%20group%20that%20is%20ready%20for%20a%20fight%20to%20death.%20That%20happens%20when%20one%20has%20nothing%20to%20lose.%20The%20Pakistani%20state%20has%20taken%20away%20their%20land%2C%20their%20freedoms%2C%20their%20children%20and%20their%20health%E2%80%94half%20of%20Baloch%20children%20are%20malnourished%E2%80%94even%20while%20the%20state%20benefits%20from%20their%20abundant%20natural%20resources%2C%20particularly%20oil%20and%20gas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jaffar%20Express%2C%20with%20its%20over%20400%20passengers%2C%20was%20travelling%20from%20Quetta%20in%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20through%20the%20Punjab%20heartland%2C%20towards%20Peshawar%2C%20and%20was%20carrying%20a%20contingent%20of%20Pakistan%20army%20personnel.%20It%20was%20nothing%20unusual%3B%20the%20line%20is%20used%20often%20to%20move%20the%20personnel%20between%20provinces%20during%20the%2030-hour%20journey.%20The%20train%20has%2C%20therefore%2C%20been%20a%20target%20earlier%20as%20well%2C%20one%20of%20the%20most%20recent%20incidents%20being%20a%20suicide%20attack%20in%20November%202024.%20But%20what%20was%20impressive%20about%20this%20hijack%20was%20the%20controlled%20nature%20of%20the%20attack%2C%20with%20civilians%20released%20in%20batches%2C%20and%20hostages%20separated%20quickly%20and%20apparently%20taken%20elsewhere%2C%20also%20in%20batches.%20Reliable%20reports%20indicate%20that%20most%20civilians%20were%20not%20%E2%80%98rescued'%20by%20the%20Pakistan%20army%20but%20in%20fact%20let%20off%20by%20the%20BLA%2C%20reaching%20the%20nearest%20railway%20station%20of%20Panir%20on%20foot.%20There%20is%20also%20no%20evidence%20that%20any%20civilians%20were%20targeted.%20Reportedly%2C%20however%2C%20some%20200%20coffins%20arrived%20at%20the%20station.%20Officials%20at%20the%20site%20said%20that%2019%20military%20passengers%20were%20killed%2C%20including%20one%20police%20and%20one%20railway%20official.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Pak%20Army's%20Story%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArmy%20officials%20briefing%20the%20press%20after%20the%20hijack%20declared%20that%20four%20soldiers%20and%2021%20civilians%20were%20killed.%20They%20also%20claimed%20that%20the%20siege%20had%20ended%2C%20squarely%20blaming%20the%20Taliban%20%E2%80%98interim%20government'%20for%20the%20attack.%20It%20also%20declared%20that%20the%20operation%20had%20ended%20and%2033%20terrorists%20were%20killed%20in%20total.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BLA%2C%20however%2C%20denies%20this%2C%20saying%20intense%20fighting%20continued%20long%20after%20the%20hijack%2C%20and%20that%20it%20suffered%20several%20casualties.%20Certainly%2C%20it%20is%20unlikely%20that%20in%20such%20a%20professional%20attack%2C%20the%20insurgent%20would%20simply%20sit%20and%20wait%20to%20be%20executed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20other%20attacks%20both%20preceded%20and%20followed%20the%20hijack%2C%20all%20against%20Pakistani%20army%20installations%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Frontier%20Corps%20outpost%20in%20the%20Jandola%20of%20Tank%20district%20of%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20(KP).%20Such%20attacks%20are%20now%20a%20daily%20occurrence%3B%20Pakistani%20think%20tanks%20have%20reported%20that%20there%20was%20a%2040%25%20rise%20in%20terrorist%20attacks%20last%20year%2C%20with%20more%20than%20685%20soldiers%20killed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20this%20lends%20veracity%20to%20warnings%20given%20by%20people%20like%20Maulana%20Fazlur%20Rehman%2C%20who%20said%20in%20Parliament%20that%20parts%20of%20Balochistan%20and%20KP%20were%20out%20of%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20army.%20Former%20Chief%20Minister%20Akhtar%20Mengal%20went%20even%20further%2C%20saying%20%E2%80%98not%20an%20inch'%20of%20the%20land%20was%20under%20the%20state's%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ESame%20Old%20Threats%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20is%20next%3F%20As%20the%20army%20warns%20that%20the%20%E2%80%98rules%20of%20the%20game%20have%20changed'%20look%20out%20for%20the%20following.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%2C%20a%20storm%20of%20violence%20raining%20down%20upon%20the%20hapless%20Baloch%20people%2C%20with%20no%20one%20spared.%20China%20will%20back%20such%20actions%2C%20having%20already%20announced%20its%20'strong%20support'%20for%20Pakistan.%20Beijing%20anyway%20has%20been%20pressing%20Pakistan%20to%20allow%20Chinese%20troops%20to%20be%20stationed%20on%20the%20ground%2C%20which%20Islamabad%E2%80%94with%20some%20sense%E2%80%94has%20been%20refuting.%20That%20might%20change%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESecond%2C%20expect%20that%20Rawalpindi%20will%20attack%20Afghanistan%20with%20all%20available%20means%2C%20conventional%20and%20unconventional.%20That%20could%20include%20using%20parts%20of%20the%20Islamic%20State%2C%20which%20Pakistan%2C%20with%20its%20traditional%20jihadi%20play%2C%20supports%20selectively.%20At%20the%20UN%2C%20the%20Taliban%20have%20complained%20that%20%E2%80%98certain%20countries'%20are%20acting%20vindictively%20against%20them%2C%20even%20as%20Pakistan's%20Permanent%20Representative%20accused%20the%20Taliban%20of%20sheltering%20all%20manners%20of%20terrorists.%20There%20is%20also%20the%20significant%20accusation%20that%20the%20BLA%20is%20being%20trained%20by%20al%20Qaeda%20and%20the%20Islamic%20State.%20That%20is%20an%20allegation%20that%20could%20cost%20the%20Baloch%20international%20sympathy.%20In%20a%20vindication%20of%20Trump's%20accusations%20of%20a%20%E2%80%98deep%20state'%2C%20this%20particular%20charge%20is%20being%20parroted%20across%20the%20internet%20by%20some%20curious%20handles.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20truth%20is%20that%20the%20BLA%20has%20nothing%20in%20common%20with%20al%20Qaeda%20or%20ISIS.%20But%20Rawalpindi%20will%20still%20try%20to%20paint%20it%20as%20such.%20It%20has%20much%20to%20gain%2C%20after%20all.%20That%20includes%20%E2%80%98fixing'%20an%20uncooperative%20Kabul%2C%20and%20funds%20flowing%20again%20if%20the%20US%20returns%20either%20into%20or%20on%20the%20borders%20of%20Afghanistan.%20That%20ultimately%20means%20Pakistani%20intelligence%20and%20airfields%20for%20hire.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere's%20the%20crux%20of%20the%20whole%20thing%3A%20there%20has%20never%20been%20a%20train%20hijack%20in%20living%20memory%20in%20recent%20years.%20That%20means%20the%20BLA%20now%20gets%20the%20international%20spotlight.%20Whether%20or%20not%20that%20is%20a%20good%20thing%20depends%20on%20international%20sympathy.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20indomitable%20Mehrang%20Baloch%20has%20been%20nominated%20for%20the%20Nobel%20Peace%20Prize%20in%202025.%20Another%20two%20fighters%20for%20Baloch%20rights%2C%20Mama%20Qadeer%20Baloch%20and%20Nargis%20Baloch%2C%20have%20been%20nominated%20for%20the%20Nelson%20Mandela%20Peace%20Prize%2C%20a%20huge%20honour%20at%20any%20level.%20Slowly%20but%20surely%2C%20the%20Baloch%20cause%20is%20gaining%20recognition%20in%20international%20circles.%20Pakistan%20could%20come%20under%20pressure%20to%20give%20them%20some%20rights.%20However%2C%20so%20far%2C%20its%20fall-back%20option%20is%20the%20usual%20one%3A%20accuse%20everyone%20else%20and%20get%20what%20it%20wants%20the%20most%2C%20world%20attention%20and%20funds.%20Given%20the%20depressing%20repetition%20of%20policy%2C%20that%20might%20even%20just%20happen.%20But%20the%20Baloch%20story%20is%20not%20over.%20All%20of%20this%20will%20only%20add%20fuel%20to%20the%20fire.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Tara%20Kartha%20is%20a%20former%20director%20of%20the%20National%20Security%20Council%20Secretariat)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742192580000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fuqgqddb_jaffer-express_625x300_13_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fafter-the-pakistan-train-terror-the-story-is-just-beginning-7941091%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20whole%20episode%20lends%20veracity%20to%20warnings%20given%20by%20people%20like%20Maulana%20Fazlur%20Rehman%2C%20who%20said%20in%20Parliament%20that%20parts%20of%20Balochistan%20and%20KP%20were%20out%20of%20the%20control%20of%20the%20Pakistan%20army.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fafter-the-pakistan-train-terror-the-story-is-just-beginning-7941091%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHid%20Gold%20Wherever%20She%20Had...%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20MLA's%20Vulgar%20Remarks%20Against%20Ranya%20Rao%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20BJP%20legislator%20in%20Karnataka%20known%20for%20his%20outspoken%20comments%20has%20set%20off%20a%20new%20controversy%20with%20vulgar%20remarks%20about%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DRanya-Rao%5C%22%3ERanya%20Rao%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Kannada%20actor%20facing%20a%20gold%20smuggling%20probe%20after%20being%20caught%20at%20the%20airport%20two%20weeks%20ago.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fsearch%3Fsearchtext%3DBasangouda-Patil-Yatnal%5C%22%3EBasangouda%20Patil%20Yatnal%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20an%20MLA%20from%20Bijapur%20City%2C%20made%20the%20remarks%20over%20an%20alleged%20gold%20smuggling%20attempt%20by%20the%20actor%20and%20claimed%20he%20knew%20which%20ministers%20were%20involve