nformation%20about%20her%20relationships%2C%20who%20helped%20her%20obtain%20security%20(clearance)%2C%20and%20how%20the%20gold%20was%20brought%20in.%20I%20will%20expose%20everything%20in%20the%20session%2C%20including%20which%20hole%20she%20hid%20the%20gold%20and%20brought%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20D%20K%20Shivakumar%20had%20earlier%20rejected%20the%20involvement%20of%20any%20of%20his%20ministers%20in%20the%20smuggling%20case%20as%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20gossip%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Patil%20is%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fkarnataka-news%2Fbjp-high-command-told-me-not-to-speak-against-bs-yediyurappa-karnataka-mla-basangouda-patil-yatnal-3728401%5C%22%3Enot%20new%20to%20controversies%3C%2Fa%3E.%20His%20latest%20remark%20follows%20his%20repeated%20criticism%20of%20state%20unit%20chief%20BY%20Vijayendra%2C%20the%20son%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20BS%20Yediyurappa.%20He%20had%20also%20called%20for%20Mr%20Yediyurappa's%20removal%20when%20he%20was%20the%20chief%20minister.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20he%20was%20issued%20a%20notice%20by%20the%20Election%20Commission%20for%20labelling%20Congress%20leader%20Sonia%20Gandhi%20as%20%26quot%3Bvishkanya%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202020%2C%20Mr%20Yatnal%20had%20praised%20a%20decision%20to%20scrap%20a%20wedding%20scheme%20for%20poor%20women%20from%20minority%20communities%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bthose%20who%20want%20the%20scheme%20can%20go%20to%20Pakistan%26quot%3B.%20He%20had%20also%20sparked%20a%20controversy%20by%20branding%20a%20freedom%20fighter%2C%20who%20died%20at%20103%20a%20year%20later%2C%20a%20%26quot%3BPakistani%20agent%26quot%3B%20for%20his%20stand%20on%20the%20citizenship%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1742191980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fikfji89o_ranya-rao_625x300_11_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-mla-basangouda-patil-yatnals-vulgar-remark-against-ranya-rao-in-gold-smuggling-case-7940957%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20BJP%20legislator%20in%20Karnataka%20known%20for%20his%20outspoken%20comments%20has%20set%20off%20a%20new%20controversy%20with%20vulgar%20remarks%20about%20Ranya%20Rao%2C%20the%20Kannada%20actor%20facing%20a%20gold%20smuggling%20probe%20after%20being%20caught%20at%20the%20airport%20two%20weeks%20ago.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbjp-mla-basangouda-patil-yatnals-vulgar-remark-against-ranya-rao-in-gold-smuggling-case-7940957%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHafiz%20Saeed%20May%20Face%20Similar%20Fate%26quot%3B%3A%20Expert%20As%20Nephew%20Killed%20In%20Pakistan%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFollowing%20the%20assassination%20of%20Lashkar-e-Taiba%20(LeT)%20terrorist%20Abu%20Qatal%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20foreign%20affairs%20experts%20have%20suggested%20that%20Hafiz%20Saeed%2C%20the%20mastermind%20behind%20the%2026%2F11%20Mumbai%20attacks%2C%20might%20face%20a%20%26quot%3Bsimilar%20fate%26quot%3B%20soon.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20with%20the%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20Robinder%20Sachdeva%20said%20that%20Abu%20Qatal's%20killing%20indicates%20that%20those%20tracking%20LeT%20founder%20Hafiz%20Saeed%20and%20other%20terrorists%20are%20closing%20in.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHafiz%20Saeed's%20close%20aide%20was%20killed%2C%20which%20means%20those%20who%20are%20tracking%20them%20have%20reached%20quite%20close.%20It%20is%20said%20that%20those%20who%20live%20by%20the%20sword%20die%20by%20the%20sword%2C%20and%20Hafiz%20Saeed%20might%20as%20well%20have%20to%20face%20a%20similar%20fate.%20Abu%20Qatal%20was%20involved%20in%20a%20lot%20of%20attacks%20in%20Kashmir%2C%20Rajouri%2C%20Poonch%2C%20PoK%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sachdeva%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sachdeva%20speculated%20that%20Saeed%20might%20have%20tightened%